#

Spiced Minced Pork Stir-Fry

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinLow-CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

PorkStir-FryQuick MealHealthy

Description

A vibrant stir-fry featuring savory minced pork and fresh vegetables, bursting with spices for a deliciously satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Minced Pork: 1 lb
  • Bell Peppers: 1 cup, sliced
  • Carrots: 1 cup, julienned
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Soy Sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Sesame Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Green Onions: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Red Chili Flakes: 1 tsp
  • Olive Oil: 1 tbsp
